properties.value: Skull could refer to any of the following:

content:
The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on: rsw:Skull

Skull could refer to any of the following:

  • Animal skull, one of 2 quest items.
  • Monkey skull, a rare item that can be used to make a blue face gorilla Greegree.
  • Ghost's skull, a quest item.
  • Skulls, a scenery object.
  • Skull (item), an item with various uses.
  • Skull (status), a status affecting items kept on death.
  • Skull sceptre, a player-made staff that is able to teleport to Barbarian Village.
    • Strange skull, one of the components required to make the staff.
    • Right skull half, an item used to make the full skull.
    • Left skull half, an item used to make the full skull.
  • Skull torches, a decoration a player can build in their POH.
  • Werewolf Skullball, an Agility related activity.
  • Skull slope found within the Ape Atoll Agility Course.
